margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;"><section style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 25px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-top-left-radius: 50%; border-top-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-left-radius: 50%; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="yead_color" style="color: rgb(58, 188, 255); font-size: 18px;">★</span></section></section><section class="yead_bdtc yead_bdbc" style="margin-top: -16px; margin-bottom: -16px; padding: 20px 10px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 50);"><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; color: inherit; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color:inherit"></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">唐雪妹</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">，</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">数学与信息（软件）</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">学院</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">2013</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">级</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">统计学专业</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">学生。</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">第二届模范引领计划数学与信息学院学习之星获得者。</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">现</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">任学院团委组织部干事</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">，现任班级</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">团支书</span><span style="font-size: 24px;">。</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri;"><img data-w="24" data-ratio="1" style="float: left;" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650959078.png"/><br/></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri;"><br/></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 79, 121); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">人生格言：以学为友，以梦为马，定不负韶华。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri;"></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);">获奖情况</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;">：</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">1. 2014-2015年度国家励志奖学金、校级一等</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">奖学金及“三好学生标兵”称号<br/></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> 2. 2013-2014年度国家励志奖学金、校级二等</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">奖学金及“三好学生”称号<br/></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;2. 2015年全国大学生数学建模竞赛广东省赛</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">区二等奖</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;3.华南农业大学第十一届数学建模竞赛三等奖</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;4. 2014-2015年度社会调研协会第七届调查大</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;">赛二</span><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">等奖</span></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;5. 2013年度、2014年度华南农业大学优秀共 </span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">青团干部称号</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;6.第十届中华状元红知识竞技大赛优秀奖</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;7.中国扶贫基金会二星级善行<span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri;">100 </span>志愿者称号</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;8.《思想道德修养与法律基础》社会实践调研</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">大赛二等奖</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;"><img data-w="24" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650959074.png"/><br/> </span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;"></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px;"> &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">在两年的大学学习以来，她以踏实专注、勤思善</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">思的学习态度在学习上取得了好成绩，连续两年以</span><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4.0</span>以上的绩点位列专业前三名，综合测评均为专业第一</span><span style="font-size: 5px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;">.<br/></span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px;"> &nbsp; <span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">在夯实专业知识的基础的道路上，她积极参</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px;">加各种知识竞赛，力图用竞赛来锻炼提高创新能力。她参与的创新训练计划项目“基于互联网技术的大学生创业研究”成为国家级项目之一，参与的全</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;">国大学生数学建模获广东省赛区二等奖等；</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px;">同时作为团支书，她获得校级优秀共青团干部称号，起到学生干部的模范带头作用，积极引导同学提高学习的热情。</span></p></section><section style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 25px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-top-left-radius: 50%; border-top-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-left-radius: 50%; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle;"><span class="yead_color" style="color: rgb(58, 188, 255); font-size: 18px;">★</span></section></section></section></section><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style=""><section style="border: none rgb(255, 129, 36); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="margin: 5px auto;"><section class="yead_bdlc" style="color: inherit; font-size: 16px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 35px; margin-left: 27px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(58, 188, 255);"><section class="yead_bgc" style="width: 26px; height: 26px; margin-left: -50px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; background-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">一</section><section style="margin-top:-26px;color:inherit;clear:both;line-height:30px;font-size:14px;color:inherit"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> 图文来源：唐雪妹</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"> 编辑：思源工作室 郑晓莹<br/></span></p><p><br/></p></section><section class="yead_bgc" style="width: 10px; height: 10px; margin-left: -40px; margin-top: -14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; background-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><br/><p><br/></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></p>');
