(7, '采访', '陈学凡，中共党员，数学与信息学院2013级计算机科学与技术专业学生。第二届模范引领计划数学与信息学院学干之星获得者。曾任数学与信息学院团委秘书长，现担任学院本科生计算机科学与技术第二党支部副书记，班级学习委员，2015级计算机科学与技术4班助理班主任。\r\n', 'http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/1465095989000913.JPG', 1465096136, 1465096136, '陈学凡', '模范引领', '秉承“服务同学”宗旨，谱写学生工作华章', '<p><em class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" style="margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(140, 140, 140); max-width: none; font-style: normal; "></em><br/></p><p><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none; font-family: 微软雅黑; "><section style="margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(197, 200, 204); text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 1px 0px, rgb(197, 200, 204) 0px 2px 0px, rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px, rgb(197, 200, 204) 0px 4px 0px; "><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 25px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(197, 200, 204); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(219, 219, 221); "><section style="margin-right: 100px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; height: 14px; width: 14px; border-top-left-radius: 7px; border-top-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-left-radius: 7px; background-color: rgb(173, 173, 173); "><section style="margin-top: 30px; max-width: 100%; box-s