-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 21px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">陈学凡，中共党员，数学与信息学院2013级计算机科学与技术专业学生。第二届模范引领计划数学与信息学院学干之星获得者。曾任数学与信息学院团委秘书长，现担任学院本科生计算机科学与技术第二党支部副书记，班级学习委员，2015级计算机科学与技术4班助理班主任。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 21px; "><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri; "><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650960240.png" data-ratio="0.7593283582089553" data-w="536" data-src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/zUmAsOic50wAYhqyiaxTc0GQ58LENpxmsgcro1EDAial4Oib1jc5LjibqAlCQZy3WWFO0eD1kEum7aowayRVMRCLwDg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" style="box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; width: 745px; visibility: visible ! important; height: 573px;" height="573" width="745"/></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 24px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 24px; font-family: Calibri; "></span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 79, 121); font-family: 宋体; ">人生格言：成功无捷径，立志存高远。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); ">获奖情况： &nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">1、2013-2014年度校级一等奖学金并获得“三好学生标兵” &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">2、2014-2015年度校级二等奖学金并获得“三好学生”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">3、2014-2015年度校级“优秀团干部标兵”、院级“优秀团干部”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">4、2013-2014年度华南农业大学“优秀团员”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">5、2013-2014年度数学与信息学院团委学生会“优秀干事”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">6、2013-2014年度校学生工作通讯社“第一学期优秀社员”、“十月份优秀社员”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">7、2015年全国井冈山青少年教育基地“井冈情▪中国梦”暑期专项行动优秀学员及优秀团队</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">8、2014-2015年度广东省“远标杯”C语言竞赛优秀志愿者</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">9、2013-2014年度广东省“凯通杯”JAVA省赛优秀志愿者</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">10、2014-2015年度广东省优秀社团成员</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">11、2013-2014年度校学生工作通讯社《屋檐》征文三等奖</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; "><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; ">12、2013-2014年度院际女子排球赛获团体第6名</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 17px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "> </span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650960252.png" data-ratio="0.7145522388059702" data-w="536" data-src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/zUmAsOic50wAYhqyiaxTc0GQ58LENpxmsg0nBTl9AlqmMGZMUhxDPicRU90hlhclicgibPo1CXEreOc1RAqEpoD0XrQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" style="box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 775px; visibility: visible ! important; height: 603px;" height="603" width="775"/></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">担任学院团委秘书长期间，她参与组织、策划广东省“远标杯”C语言竞赛、第十一届“IT文化节”、2014级新生迎新工作、学院双代会、“我来代言”晚会暨班级风采大赛等一系列院级省级大型活动。在活动组织过程中，她兢兢业业，认真做好活动中的每个细节，受到老师与同学们的一致好评，多次获得华南农业大学“优秀团干部标兵”</span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">、学院“优秀团干部”、省赛“优秀志愿者”等荣誉称号。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32px; "><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; "></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">在团委学生会的工作期间，她不断地挑战自我，并且在工作中不断寻求创新和突破。例如在负责华南农业大学紫荆科技文化节学院</span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">摆摊活动期间，她精心规划了学院摊位的摊位布置，增设“紫荆文化节”系列精美明信片、徽章和卡贴，形成系列宣传；并且</span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; ">将学院学子自己创作的游戏放在摊位上展示。“高山仰止，景行行止。”面对比其强大许多的人与事，她一直都保持着敬畏的心态，并且在其工作中更好地体现个人价值。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 17px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; "> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;她热心公益，积极参加社会实践，努力提升综合素养。她曾参加2014年7月暑期桂林下乡活动，所在团队获得“校级优秀下乡团队”称号。此外，她作为校第四期青马班优秀学员代表，参加了2015年全国井冈山青少年教育基地“井冈情▪中国梦”暑期专项行动，与全国20余所知名高校展开交流，并在此次实践季活动中获得“优秀团队”和“优秀学员”称号。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br/></span></p></section><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); display: inline-block; "><section style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 25px; height: 25px; border-top-left-radius: 50%; border-top-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-right-radius: 50%; border-bottom-left-radius: 50%; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; "><span class="yead_color" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(58, 188, 255); font-size: 18px; ">★</span></section></section></section></section><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: none rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); "><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section class="yead_bdlc" style="margin-left: 27px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 35px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); "><section class="yead_bgc" style="margin-left: -50px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 26px; height: 26px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; background-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); ">一</section><section style="margin-top: -26px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; clear: both; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; "><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; "><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; "> 图文来源：</span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; ">陈学凡</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; "><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; "> 编辑：思源工作室 李君玉<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "/></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; "><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "/></p></section><section class="yead_bgc" style="margin-top: -14px; margin-left: -40px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 10px; height: 10px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; background-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); "><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "/><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; "><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "/></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; "><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; "/></p></section></section></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p>'),
(8, '采访', '王朝鹏，数学与信息学院学院14级计算机科学与技术专业学生。2014-2015国家奖学金获得者,第二届模范引领计划数学与信息学院华农之星获得者。现任班级心理委员。', 'http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/146509606900014.png', 1465096238, 1465096238, '王朝鹏', '模范引领', '没有追求和付出，哪来的成功', '<section label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><section style="margin-top:.5em;margin-bottom:.5em;box-sizing:border-box"><section style=" margin-top:.5em;margin-bottom:.5em;text-align:center; height:100% "><img style="vertical-align:middle" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650961805.png" data-ratio="0.15" data-w="400"/><section style="padding:.5em"><section><section style="  height:100% "><section style="font-size:16px;color:#2A343A"><section style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#333;line-height:30px"><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;color: rgb(149, 55, 52);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important">数学与信息（软件）学院</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">模范引领计划华农之星获得者</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;color: rgb(149, 55, 52);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);font-size: 18px;text-indent: 28px"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 20px;line-height: 32px">王朝鹏</span></span></span></p></span></section></section></section></section></section><p><img style="vertical-align:middle" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650961800.png" data-ratio="0.15" data-w="400"/></p><section label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="font-family: 5px auto"><section style="font-family: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑"><section style=";padding: 0px;-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);display: inline-block"><section style=";padding: 0px;width: 25px;height: 25px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-top-left-radius: 50%;border-top-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;display: table-cell;vertical-align: middle"><span style="color: rgb(112, 216, 255);font-size: 18px">★</span></section></section><section class="yead_bdtc yead_bdbc" style="font-family: -16px 0px;padding: 20px 10px;border-top-width: 1px;border-top-style: solid;border-top-color: rgb(112, 216, 255);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;border-bottom-color: rgb(112, 216, 255);color: rgb(51, 51, 50)"><p style="margin-bottom: 17px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 21px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">王朝鹏，数学与信息学院学院</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">14</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">级计算机科学与技术专业学生。2014-2015国家奖学金获得者,第二届模范引领计划数学与信息学院华农之星获得者。现任班级心理委员。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 17px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 18px;">人生格言：深窥自己的内心，而后发觉一切奇迹在你自己。</span><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650961818.png" data-ratio="0.8415637860082305" data-w="486" style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">获奖情况：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">1、2014-2015年度国奖奖学金</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">2、2014-2015年“电机工程学会杯”全国大学生数学建模竞赛国家二等奖</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">3、第八届“认证杯”数学建模网络挑战赛全国比赛省级一等奖</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">4、“高教社杯”全国大学生数学建模竞赛省级二等奖</span></p><p style="margin-top: 7px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">5、华南农业大学思政部社会调研成果赛二等奖</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 17px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 21px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:17px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:left"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">他学习成绩优异，专业绩点名列前茅。无论是专业课还是非专业课，他都积极配合任课老师，回答任课老师所提出的问题，多次组织同学，脚踏实地地完成老师所布置的调研、讲课任务，得到了老师和同学的认可。他是班级两届的心理委员，在自己的岗位上认真负责，发动全班拍摄心理</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">DV</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">剧，细心留意班级同学的心理问题并及时予以心理辅导。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:7px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:17px;margin-left:0;margin-top:auto;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">他热爱学术竞赛，认为大学光靠理论知识是远远不够的。他五次参加数学建模竞赛，四次获奖，获得国家级奖项一项，省级奖项三项，然而这并不能满足他对于专业知识灵活运用于实战中的要求，他还参与了“汇丰杯”SAS</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体;">数据分析大赛，</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Calibri;">ACM</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体;">校赛。</span></span></p><p style="margin: auto 0px 17px; text-indent: 32px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">除\r\n此之外，他爱演讲，爱文学，爱志愿活动，也是一名植物爱好者。他多次参加演讲、调研答辩比赛并取得不错的成绩；参加征文比赛，挥洒自己的文笔；积极参加学\r\n院内、学校内、校外多次志愿活动，希望能够以一己薄力帮助别人；他爱植物，是学校植物观赏协会的技术部部长，策划举办大型植物活动，传播华农的自然之美。</span><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14650961819.png" data-ratio="0.8209876543209876" data-w="486"/></p></section><section style=";padding: 0px;-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);display: inline-block"><section style=";padding: 0px;width: 25px;height: 25px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-top-left-radius: 50%;border-top-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;display: table-cell;vertical-align: middle"><span style="color: rgb(112, 216, 255);font-size: 18px">★</span></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p></section></section></section>');

