clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">梦想，从&quot;源&quot;开始。</span><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved."><section style="margin:0 auto;padding: 10px 10px;border-style: none;"><span style="float: left;margin-left: -7px;margin-top: 15px;display: block;"><section class="yead_bgc" style="max-height: 30px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); line-height: 1.5; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 10px; padding: 5px 8px; min-width: 75px;">思源简介<br/></section><img data-w="7" data-ratio="0.8571428571428571" data-type="png" style="display: block;width: 7px;" src="http://7xlp0l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14648567009.png"/></span><section style="padding: 16px;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);-moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);-o-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.4;"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"> &nbsp; 思源工作室（原助学管理委员会）成立于<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2011</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">10</span>月,是一个独立于学院院团委学生会、由学院辅导员直接指导的学生组织。工作室以服务师生，奉献社会为宗旨！主要负责学院贫困生入库、奖助贷、勤工助学等工作，管理全院近1000名家庭经济困难学生的相关工作，组织定期开展志愿服务感恩活动，收集和反馈学生意见，搭建学生与学院交流的平台。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;工作室在主任团下设有助贷部、秘书部，勤工部、宣传部及实践部<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Times New Roman;">5</span>个部门，主任团带领各部门统筹思源工作室相关工作，对内做好沟通协调，增强团队凝聚力，负责监督、评估各部门工作质量，并规划工作室的未来发展以及与学院辅导员和校勤工助学管理中心的沟通协调工作。</span></p></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/zUmAsOic50wAwVgPOJxc5CpLsTOiaQQdm7HXuGN7orx08f5OdrdgZichkThhXdibOqicLnvEzzjdr2NRzmE4wUWSOSg/640?wx_fmt=png&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" style="width: auto ! important; visibility: visible ! important; height: auto ! important;" data-w="" data-ratio="0.27722772277227725" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/zUmAsOic50wAwVgPOJxc5CpLsTOiaQQdm7HXuGN7orx08f5OdrdgZichkThhXdibOqicLnvEzzjdr2NRzmE4wUWSOSg/0?wx_fmt=png"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="border:none;border-style:none;margin: 1em auto;width: 100%;"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><section class="main" style="border: medium none rgb(58, 188, 255); margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;"><section class="main2" data-brushtype="text" style="color: rgb(58, 188, 255); font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 3px; padding: 9px 4px 14px; text-align: center; margin: 0px auto; border: 4px solid rgb(58, 188, 255); border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box;">部门职能<span class="main3" data-brushtype="text" style="display: block; font-size: 10px; line-height: 12px; border-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">BUMENZHINEN</span> &nbsp;<br/></section><section class="main4" style="width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; border-top: 0.6em solid rgb(58, 188, 255); border-bottom-color: rgb(58, 188, 255); height: 10px; color: inherit; border-left: 0.7em solid transparent ! important; border-right: 0.7em solid transparent ! important; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" data-width="0px"></section></section></section></section><section class="yead_editor" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved." style="border:none;border-style:none;margin: 1em auto;width: 100%;"><h2 style="margin:8px 0 0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;white-spa